'''Kathy Burdette''' contributed two source articles to the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]'' and wrote the short story "[[Gathering Shadows]]" for the ''[[Tales from the New Republic]]'' anthology. She also illustrated several articles for the journal and was the featured artist for [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 11|issue 11]].

She lives in [[Wikipedia:Williamsburg, Virginia|Williamsburg, Virginia]] and is Senior Project Editor of Book Publications for the Omohundro Institute of Early American History and Culture.
